description: Kathie & Angela Marmo, a talented mother & daughter-in-law team, are serving Rochester’s favorite pastries on the streets, courtesy of this neat truck. Their signature Beignets, French Macarons, and Creme Brûlée are delicious and perfect for every kind of event or party, so if you and your guests are craving something super tasty, then look no further than Sweet Sammie Jane’s.
name: Sweet Sammie Jane's
